article.description: Bryson Williams registered 16 points as UTEP edged past Ball State 71-70 in the Diamond Head Classic on Monday night.
article.headline: Williams scores 16 to lift UTEP past Ball State 71-70
article.linkText: Williams scores 16 to lift UTEP past Ball State 71-70
article.story: HONOLULU -- Bryson Williams registered 16 points as UTEP edged past Ball State 71-70 in the Diamond Head Classic on Monday night. Efe Odigie added 12 points and Kaden Archie had 11 for UTEP (9-3). Jarron Coleman, Ishmael El-Amin, and Tahjai Teague each scored 14 points for the Cardinals (6-6). --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
